    "body": "@catamorphism I just don't see how #2189 means 'we will never have it again', all comments there read as 'syntax is convenient, but impl should not be something separate from a closure', heck you self said basically the same there ;)\nOf course the language requirements change over time, but... I don't see the harm here? Syntactically it would be a fully backwards compatible change to re-add it.\n",
